remarks as "serious and bold," adding that "the remarks expressed
the pro-peace stance of France and Europe that will help
effectively save the Middle East peace process."
</P>
<P>
France, which ruled Lebanon between the two World Wars, has
been enjoying a good relationship with Lebanon. 
