<TEXT>
<P>
BUDAPEST, June 6 (Xinhua) -- Hungary's Federation of Young
Democrats-Hungarian Civic Party (Fidesz-MPP) has decided Saturday
to form a coalition government with the Hungarian Democratic Forum
(HDF) and the Independent Smallholders' and Peasants' Party (ISPP).
</P>
<P>
The decision was reached at the tenth national congress of
Fidesz-MPP.
</P>
<P>
