Viktor, noted that his party will play the leading role in the new
troika administration which will be full of confidence and well
staffed.
</P>
<P>
Negotiations have run smoothly between the Fidesz-MPP and the
HDF on the preparation work for the coalition.
</P>
<P>
However, that with the ISPP, scheduled to start next week, are
expected to be tough.
</P>
<P>
The right-wing Fidesz-MPP won 148 out of the 386 seats of the
unicameral National Assembly (parliament) in the two rounds of
legislative elections held on May 10 and 24.
</P>
<P>
The ISPP and the HDF netted 48 and 17 respectively. 
