million Dollars) was still needed to reach the proposed 100
million Rand (19.6 million dollars) operating budget.
</P>
<P>
"I can see my staff smiling because we can move forward,"
committee chief executive Danie Malan said, adding "but we still
need a lot of support to make the book balance".
</P>
<P>
The national government, the Gauteng province and the
Johannesburg metropolitan authorities have pledged to contribute a
further 31 million Rand (6.1 million dollars) in support services
and facilities, the report said.
